snippet.title: KILL la KILL - IF - English Play Guide
snippet.description:
Learn how to play the brand new eye-popping anime fighting game from Arc System Works, KILL la KILL - IF, in this quick guide to the game's controls and mechanics!

Pre-order now!
Switch - https://www.amazon.co.uk/KILL-IF-Nintendo-Switch/dp/B07P74X8Q2/ref=sr_1_1?keywords=kill+la+kill+if&qid=1554890769&s=gateway&sr=8-1
PS4 - https://www.amazon.co.uk/KILL-LA-IF-PS4/dp/B07P74XNTB/ref=sr_1_2?keywords=kill+la+kill+if&qid=1554890769&s=gateway&sr=8-2

Learn more here: http://pqube.co.uk/kill-la-kill/

Come chat to us on our PQube Discord server! https://discord.gg/xHS7MnU
